## 📂 Repository Layout

```
kubernetesArchitecture/
├── alerting-app/               # Alert-analyzer Flask app (Dockerfile + prometheus-webhook.py)
├── ansible/
│   ├── ansible.cfg
│   ├── inventory/hosts.yaml
│   └── playbooks/
│       ├── setupkube.yaml      # Main cluster deployment playbook
│       ├── setupgit.yaml       # GitLab CE + pipeline setup playbook
│       ├── setadmin.yaml       # AWS profile configuration helper
│       └── teardown.yaml       # Full teardown playbook
├── gitlab/
│   ├── pipeline-config/        # GitLab Agent config.yaml
│   └── runner/runner-role.yaml # CloudFormation: GitLab Runner IAM role
└── kubernetes/
    ├── autoscaler/             # Cluster Autoscaler Helm values + CloudFormation IAM role
    ├── default/                # Application pods, services, PostgreSQL StatefulSet, EFS CSI role
    ├── ingress/                # NGINX Ingress resources, DNS/TLS CloudFormation, kustomization
    └── monitoring/
        ├── alerting/           # Alert-analyzer pod, service account, SNS CloudFormation
        ├── loki/               # Loki Helm values + LogQL alert rules
        ├── prometheus/         # Prometheus, Alertmanager, Grafana Helm values
        └── promtail/           # Promtail Helm values
```
